            "creation_date": 1393843265,
            "body": "<p>Looking at the Settings panel that Maheshbabu Jammula posted, you can see an Inline Elements list. Just remove <code>&lt;tr&gt;<\/code> and <code>&lt;td&gt;<\/code> tags from the list and those tags will always land in a new line. Take Care! <\/p>\n\n<p>Preferences > Web > HTML Files > Editor<\/p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/483mE.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 22144545,
            "question_id": 22139262
        },
